# <type>: <subject>
#
# =============================================
# Conventional Commits Format
# =============================================
#
# Types:
#   feat     - New feature (新機能)
#   fix      - Bug fix (バグ修正)
#   docs     - Documentation only (ドキュメント)
#   style    - Formatting, no code change (フォーマット)
#   refactor - Code restructure, no behavior change (リファクタリング)
#   perf     - Performance improvement (性能改善)
#   test     - Adding tests (テスト追加)
#   build    - Build system changes (ビルド)
#   ci       - CI configuration (CI設定)
#   chore    - Maintenance, dependencies (メンテナンス)
#   revert   - Revert previous commit (リバート)
#
# =============================================
# Subject Guidelines
# =============================================
#
# - Use imperative mood: "add" not "added" or "adds"
# - No period at the end
# - Max 50 characters
# - Capitalize first letter (optional but consistent)
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add VPC module for production environment
#   fix: correct security group ingress rule
#   docs: update README with setup instructions
#   refactor: simplify error handling in main.tf
#   chore: update terraform to version 1.14.3
#
# =============================================
# Body (Optional)
# =============================================
#
# - Wrap at 72 characters
# - Explain what and why, not how
# - Separate from subject with blank line
#
# Example:
#
#   feat: add VPC module for production environment
#
#   This module creates a VPC with public and private subnets
#   across multiple availability zones. It follows the company's
#   network architecture standards for production workloads.
#
#   The module outputs VPC ID and subnet IDs for downstream
#   resources to reference.
#
# =============================================
# Footer (Optional)
# =============================================
#
# - Reference issues: Closes #123, Fixes #456
# - Breaking changes: BREAKING CHANGE: description
# - Co-authors: Co-authored-by: Name <email>
#
# Example:
#
#   Closes #123
#   Related to #456
#   BREAKING CHANGE: remove deprecated output variables
#
# =============================================
# Japanese Style Examples (日本語スタイル)
# =============================================
#
# If your team uses Japanese commit messages:
#
#   feat: VPC モジュールを追加
#   fix: セキュリティグループのルールを修正
#   docs: デプロイ手順書を更新
#
# Or mixed style:
#
#   feat: add VPC module (VPCモジュール追加)
#
